collection.description: This collection features our conversations throughout the State of Maine held with educators, students, community members, and major Maine industry professionals. We are asking what youth will need to thrive personally, civically, and economically in the Maine of 2050. The collection is expanding daily, so check back!
collection.title: Maine ED 2050

highlights.description: Family child care providers are early childhood educator and care professionals. We may not be educators in a public school, but we are part of the larger education field.
What use to be seen as a center only issue is now impacting family child care as providers are trying to expand the care opportunities they can provide. Staff is needed for that to happen.

title: FCCAM Board Child Care Industry Conversation
